---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageTitle from "../components/PageTitle.astro";
import SkillElement from "../components/SkillElement.astro";
import Location from "../components/Location.astro";
import SocialLinks from "../components/SocialLinks.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - TobWeb">
    <PageTitle>About Me</PageTitle>

    <div class="flex gap-4 mb-8 -mt-4">
        <SocialLinks/>
    </div>

    <a href="https://byron.ch" target="_blank" class="block mb-8">
        <div class="card hover:bg-base-300 bg-base-100 dark:hover:bg-base-200 dark:bg-base-300 shadow-sm group">
            <div class="card-body">
                <time class="font-mono italic font-bold">2025 - Present</time>

                <h2 class="card-title">
                    Full-Stack Software Developer · Byron Informatik AG
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"
                         class="inline-block h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform
                     group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:translate-x-1
                     motion-reduce:transition-none ml-1 translate-y-px" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.22 14.78a.75.75 0 001.06 0l7.22-7.22v5.69a.75.75 0 001.5 0v-7.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-7.5a.75.75 0 000 1.5h5.69l-7.22 7.22a.75.75 0 000 1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4">I'm developing software solutions on the basis of various modern technologies.
                    My current work focuses on <i>byronFM</i>, a leading SaaS product for computer-aided facility management (CAFM).
                    My responsibilities include designing architectures for new product modules and turning complex workflows into intuitive, reliable features.
                    This includes preparing floor plans for visualization in the software and integrating AI-supported assistance.</p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 ">
                        <div class="badge badge-outline badge-primary">C#</div>
                        <div class="badge badge-outline badge-primary">Typescript</div>
                        <div class="badge badge-outline badge-primary">SQL</div>
                        <div class="badge badge-outline badge-primary">ASP.NET Core</div>
                        <div class="badge badge-outline badge-primary">Angular</div>
                        <div class="badge badge-outline badge-primary">Docker</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>


    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-8 font-bold">My Education</h2>

    <ul class="timeline timeline-vertical timeline-snap-icon timeline-compact mb-8">
        <li>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
                <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        class="text-primary h-5 w-5"
                >
                    <path
                            fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd"
                    />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-end mb-10">
                <time class="font-mono italic font-bold">2025</time>
                <div class="text-lg font-extrabold">Master's Degree in Computer Science</div>
                <Location text="University of Basel" class="mb-2"></Location>
                I pursued the Distributed Systems specialization as my Major and completed it with excellent academic
                results.
                My <a href="projects/master-thesis" class="link link-primary">Master's thesis</a> focused on enhancing the Polypheny project through the development of novel
                multi-model data pipelines.
            </div>
            <hr class="bg-primary"/>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
                <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        class="text-primary h-5 w-5"
                >
                    <path
                            fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd"
                    />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-end mb-10">
                <time class="font-mono italic font-bold">2023</time>
                <div class="text-lg font-extrabold">Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science</div>
                <Location text="University of Basel" class="mb-2"></Location>
                The Bachelor's degree has given me a strong foundation in algorithms, software engineering and
                artificial intelligence.
                In my <a href="projects/bachelor-thesis" class="link link-primary">Bachelor's thesis</a>, I integrated computational notebooks into a PolyDBMS.
            </div>
            <hr class="bg-primary"/>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
                <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        class="text-primary h-5 w-5"
                >
                    <path
                            fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd"
                    />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-end mb-10">
                <time class="font-mono italic font-bold">2020</time>
                <div class="text-lg font-extrabold">Gymnasiale Matura</div>
                <Location text="Gymnasium Laufental-Thierstein" class="mb-2"></Location>
                Completed with major subjects Applied Maths and Physics. The
                <i>Basler Maturapreis by <a class="link link-primary" href="https://www.novartis.com/">Novartis</a></i>
                awarded my outstanding academic accomplishments.
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-8 font-bold">Publications</h2>

    <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 dark:bg-base-300 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">PolyPipe: Merging Data Pipelines and Multi-Model Databases</h3>
                <p>
                    Co-authored EDBT 2026 publication based on my <a href="projects/master-thesis" class="link link-primary">Master's thesis</a>.
                </p>
                <a href="https://doi.org/10.48786/edbt.2026.72" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                   class="link link-primary w-fit">DOI: 10.48786/edbt.2026.72</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-100 dark:bg-base-300 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">PolyBooks: A System for Interactive Multi-Model Querying with Provenance and Reuse</h3>
                <p>
                    Co-authored EDBT 2026 publication based on my <a href="projects/bachelor-thesis" class="link link-primary">Bachelor's thesis</a>.
                </p>
                <a href="https://doi.org/10.48786/edbt.2026.71" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                   class="link link-primary w-fit">DOI: 10.48786/edbt.2026.71</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-8 font-bold">My Skills</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
        I consider my key strengths to be the ability to systematically analyze and solve problems, quickly grasp new
        concepts and efficiently learn new skills.
        I believe that underlying problem-solving abilities are generally more important than any specific technical skill.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-8">
        Nonetheless, the following list provides an overview of the languages and technologies I’ve worked with.
        Some of these I know very well, others I've wrestled with just enough to respect. Either way, I’m always up for
        learning more!
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mb-8 font-bold">Languages</h3>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-12 items-center justify-center mb-12">
        <SkillElement icon="java" darkIcon="java-light" title="Java"/>
        <SkillElement icon="python" title="Python"/>
        <SkillElement icon="postgresql" title="SQL"/>
        <SkillElement icon="c-plusplus" title="C++"/>
        <SkillElement icon="c-sharp" title="C#"/>
        <SkillElement icon="kotlin" title="Kotlin"/>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-12 items-center justify-center mb-8">
        <SkillElement icon="typescript" title="TypeScript"/>
        <SkillElement icon="html" title="HTML"/>
        <SkillElement icon="css" title="CSS"/>
    </div>


    <h3 class="text-2xl mb-8 font-bold">Technologies</h3>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-12 items-center justify-center mb-8">
        <SkillElement icon="git" title="Git"/>
        <SkillElement icon="angular" title="Angular"/>
        <SkillElement icon="react" title="React"/>
        <SkillElement icon="astro" title="Astro"/>
        <SkillElement icon="flask-dark" darkIcon="flask-light" title="Flask"/>
        <SkillElement icon="docker" title="Docker"/>
        <SkillElement icon="kubernetes" title="Kubernetes"/>
        <SkillElement icon="pytorch" title="PyTorch"/>
        <SkillElement icon="langchain" title="Langchain"/>
        <SkillElement icon="spark" title="Apache Spark"/>
        <SkillElement icon="mongodb-dark" darkIcon="mongodb" title="MongoDB"/>
        <SkillElement icon="neo4j" title="Neo4j"/>
        <SkillElement icon="arduino" title="Arduino"/>
    </div>
</Layout>
